review.reviewBody: Not a fan of seafood on pizza, but I had to try it and so I did. Other than that (lesson learned), everything was great.
The Best Pizza I've had in my Life
First time having "The Scott" .. Yum!  Auntie Jen nails it again!
Love the pepperoni you use on your pizzas - just the right amount of spicy! Next time I'll be sure to get a large so I have leftovers ;)
the pizza was very bland. I usually get the funky Hawaiian which is amazing. I had the Alfredo chicken and it had zero flavor. so disappointing.
